Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:04.58,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們被監視著\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We are being watched.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:06.58,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,政府有一套秘密設備…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The government has a secret system--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:11.19,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,一台每時每刻監視你的機器\N{\reng_1 - 1080}a machine that spies on you every hour of every day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:13.52,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我設計這個機器偵測恐怖行動\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I designed the machine to detect acts of terror,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:15.36,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但它卻看到了一切\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but it sees everything...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:18.23,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,普通人捲入的暴力犯罪\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Violent crimes involving ordinary people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:21.40,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,政府認為這些人無關緊要\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The government considers these people irrelevant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:23.43,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們不敢茍同\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:27.57,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,為逃避官方追捕，我們秘密行動\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hunted by the authorities, we work in secret.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:29.41,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你不可能找到我們\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You will never find us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:31.41,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但無論是受害者還是罪犯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}But victim or perpetrator,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:35.49,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,一旦你的號碼出現，我們就會找到你\N{\reng_1 - 1080}if your number's up, we'll find you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.42,0:00:45.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,快啊，沒時間了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Come on, any second, guys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:49.06,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不是時候，哈羅德\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Not a good time, Harold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:51.69,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,從來不是時候，肖女士\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It never is these days, Ms. Shaw.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:53.49,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,惠斯勒教授也有\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It's not as if Professor Whistler{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:56.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,一堆期中作業要批\N{\reng_1 - 1080}doesn't have a stack of abysmal midterms to grade.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:00:59.67,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我這裏貌似稍微緊急一些\N{\reng_1 - 1080}My situation is slightly more time sensitive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:02.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,又有新號碼出來了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And yet numbers keep coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:03.50,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,太業餘了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Amateurs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.51,0:01:06.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們最新的無關號碼叫…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Our newest irrelevant is named--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:09.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,肖女士，有人開槍嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Ms. Shaw, is that gunfire?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:11.51,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,說了我很忙的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Well, I told you I was busy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:13.38,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,現在我得讓你調出陰影圖\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now I'm gonna need you to call up that shadow map{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:16.22,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,還要獲取到紐約警局的調度信號\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and access the NYPD dispatch feeds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:17.52,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,走，走，走！\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Go, go, go, go, go! Go, go!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:25.13,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>所有人注意，追蹤黑色轎車</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}All units, pursuit in progress, black Sedan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:27.09,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>跟丟了，最後方位116街往西</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Lost them. Last seen on westbound 116.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:31.10,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>調度，10-48，這裏沒發現</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Dispatch, 10-48. No sign of them here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,漂亮\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Nice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:40.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,妞兒，擊個掌！\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yo, hottie. Up top!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:52.42,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們有約在先，記得嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We had a deal, remember?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:55.66,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你們不能拖時間，否則我就不幹了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You get out in time or I walk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:57.46,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>所以這就是後果</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}So now this happens.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.27,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Oh, God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:08.13,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,抱歉，羅密歐\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Sorry, Romeo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:10.67,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們分手了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Think we just broke up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:22.81,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,紐約警局在東河找到了你的車\N{\reng_1 - 1080}NYPD just found your getaway car by the East River.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:24.62,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,希望他們沒跟住你\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hope they can't trace it back to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.52,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,要是我銬你就難看了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Be a shame if I had to slap the cuffs on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:30.62,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你敢動我，你就難看了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Well, it's be a shame for you if you tried.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:33.36,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們要查誰？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now who's our boy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:35.49,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,托馬斯·克羅阿\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Tomas Koroa.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:37.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,美國，西班牙雙重國籍\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Dual US, Spanish citizen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:40.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>31歲，未婚</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}31 years old, unmarried.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.97,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>每年都持短期商務簽證</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Spends part of each year here{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,在紐約待一段時間\N{\reng_1 - 1080}on a B1 visa.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:47.17,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,做什麼？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Doing what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:48.81,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>國際葡萄酒貿易</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}International wine dealer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:51.21,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,主要貿易城市在紐約，倫敦\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Divides his time between New York, London,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:52.78,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,巴黎和迪拜\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Paris, and Dubai.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:55.21,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,友情提醒哦，這瓶聖艾米麗永\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now fair warning, this St. Emillion{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.68,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,會讓你們倆恨不得辭了工作\N{\reng_1 - 1080}is gonna make you both wanna quit your jobs{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:02:59.68,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>直奔波爾多</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and run way to Bordeaux.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:01.28,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,滿世界跑\N{\reng_1 - 1080}A lot of travel,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:03.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,進口外國貨\N{\reng_1 - 1080}importing foreign goods.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:05.32,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,說不定他是個走私犯呢\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Maybe he's wrapped up in smuggling.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.49,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>有可能，但是我黑了他的手機</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}That's possible, but I didn't see anything fishy{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:09.46,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,沒看到任何可疑之處\N{\reng_1 - 1080}when I bluejacked his phone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.39,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,也許他的問題跟生意無關\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Well, then maybe business isn't his problem.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:14.36,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這種人肯定到處勾搭妹子\N{\reng_1 - 1080}A guy like that could have a girl in every port.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:17.73,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,也許艷遇太多反惹一身騷\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Maybe infidelity is about to spank him on the ass.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:23.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我只是努力查找威脅，約翰\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm just trying to identify the threat, John.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:26.34,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你還是去做警探吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You just go play detective.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.35,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我能看著托馬斯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I can keep an eye on Tomas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.88,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,看出來了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I noticed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:32.15,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好吧，那芬奇呢？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}All right, well, what about Finch?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:36.05,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他不是該把托馬斯的數據資料都挖出來嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Shouldn't he be digging up Tomas' digital footprint?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:39.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他會的，但他還有別的事要先做\N{\reng_1 - 1080}He will, but he had other business to attend to first.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們現在都是雙重身份，記得嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We're all two people now, remember?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,如果你們表現好\N{\reng_1 - 1080}If you play nice on the playground,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.78,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,就能吃冰激凌，好嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}then after you will have the ice creams, yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.34,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,- 好\N- 嗯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}- Yes. - Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:08.52,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,真可愛，希望不是你的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Lovely children. Not yours, I hope.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:10.09,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,別緊張，哈羅德\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Relax, Harold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:12.92,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我只是個保姆\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm just the nanny.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:16.72,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,兩周內的第六個新身份\N{\reng_1 - 1080}My sixth new identity in two weeks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:19.39,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,應該是必要的預防措施\N{\reng_1 - 1080}A necessary precaution, I imagine,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:21.76,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,畢竟在選舉的時候你好不容易\N{\reng_1 - 1080}after your close call with Samaritan's operatives{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:23.06,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,才從撒瑪利亞的特工手裏逃出來\N{\reng_1 - 1080}during the election.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.73,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,必要是必要，但是很累\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Necessary but exhausting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.37,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,法版《歡樂滿人間》\N{\reng_1 - 1080}French Mary Poppins Barbie{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.60,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,算是我目前唯一的樂趣了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}is the only me that's been any fun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.41,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但如果孩子家長知道我殺了很多人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Though I'm not sure how the parents would feel{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:35.21,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不知道他們會作何感想\N{\reng_1 - 1080}if they knew how many people I've killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們來這幹嘛？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}So why are we here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.08,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,機器只告訴我到遊樂園來\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The machine just told me to come to this playground{\r}
