Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:45.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,希望是個好安排\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Then let's hope it's a good one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.46,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>尼古拉斯·道森</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Nicholas Dawson.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:51.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,撒瑪利亞動了手腳，讓他當了州長\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Samaritan's undemocratically elected choice for Governor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.33,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們要打倒他嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Are we bringing him down?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:56.23,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,很不幸，現在撒瑪利亞\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Unfortunately, now that Samaritan{\r}
