Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:01.64,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們不能冒險去接近新州長了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}we can't risk going anywhere near our new Governor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:04.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但我們可以暗中破壞\N{\reng_1 - 1080}But we can work to undermine{\r}
