Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.08,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,給那個人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}for that man,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:16.58,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,傑羅德·威爾金斯，軟體工程師\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Jerrod Wilkins, software engineer,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.08,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,41歲\N{\reng_1 - 1080}41 years old,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.09,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,剛離婚\N{\reng_1 - 1080}recently divorced.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.49,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,就在兩周前\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Two weeks ago,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:22.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,威爾金斯辭去了收入頗豐的技術職務\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Wilkins left a lucrative job in the tech sector{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:25.93,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,創辦了一個叫OTPS的慈善組織\N{\reng_1 - 1080}to found a new charity called OTPS.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.13,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是做什麼的？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Which stands for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.76,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,貌似沒人知道\N{\reng_1 - 1080}No one seems to know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:32.10,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,OTPS沒有辦公室，沒有官網\N{\reng_1 - 1080}OTPS has no office, no website.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們得查出他準備拿這筆錢幹什麼\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We need to find out what he plans to do with that money{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:35.30,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,然後阻止這件事\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and put a stop to it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:38.77,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,爸爸，我便便了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Daddy, I made a boom-boom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:41.27,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好吧…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Okay, um...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:43.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好，我們去…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Okay, just go ahead and--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:44.78,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,等等，等等\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Wait, hold on, hold on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.78,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,等等，別坐\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hold on, just-- Don't sit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:51.95,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,現在我知道為什麼要我扮保姆了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And now I know why I'm a nanny.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:55.19,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>再見，親愛的</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Au revoir, mon cher.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.66,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Excuse me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:04.96,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,看起來你需要一些幫助\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It seems to me as if you might need some assistance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:06.13,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好吧，六箱阿爾巴紐白葡萄酒\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Okay, so that's six cases of albariño,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:15.97,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,12箱教皇干紅，下次我去蘭斯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}12 of the neuf-du-pape, and next time I'm in Reims,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,給你帶一盒那樣的巧克力\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm sending you a box of those chocolates.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.81,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>克羅阿先生進展如何，肖女士？</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And how is Mr. Koroa faring, Ms. Shaw?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.38,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,發現威脅了嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Any sign of the threat?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:25.32,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,托馬斯四個小時只走了300米\N{\reng_1 - 1080}In four hours, Tomas has barely gone 900 feet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.49,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他只是不停地從一個餐廳走到另一個\N{\reng_1 - 1080}He just keeps moving from one restaurant to the next,{\r}
