Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>唯一讓我保持清醒的事</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The only thing keeping me awake{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:34.56,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>就是他的…</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}is his...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.76,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,個性\N{\reng_1 - 1080}personality.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.66,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Indeed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.53,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>稍等一下</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Hang on a sec.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.53,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>那姑娘今天早上在他身邊出現過</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}That's the girl who checked him out this morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,托馬斯可能被跟蹤了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Tomas may have a tail.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.17,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>這些工人早上也出現過</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Same workmen from this morning too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這不是跟蹤\N{\reng_1 - 1080}That's not a tail.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,可能是殺手小隊之類\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We're looking at some kind of a hit squad.{\r}
