Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.75,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,也可能不是殺手小隊\N{\reng_1 - 1080}this may not be that kinda hit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.23,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,十\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Ten seconds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:14.40,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,九，八，七，六\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Nine, eight, seven, six,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:18.17,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,五，四，三\N{\reng_1 - 1080}five, four, three,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:20.10,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>二，一</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}two, one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.50,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,貌似不止我們\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Looks like we're not the only ones{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.51,0:07:22.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,有雙重身份啊，芬奇\N{\reng_1 - 1080}leading double lives, Finch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:29.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>托馬斯不只是酒商，他是個賊</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Tomas isn't a wine dealer. He's a thief.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.58,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,很厲害的那種\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And a damn good one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:48.51,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>整個過程只用了十秒</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}In and out in under ten seconds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:50.02,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,完美的砸窗搶劫\N{\reng_1 - 1080}A perfect smash-and-grab.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:52.88,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,托馬斯這小子思路很清楚啊\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Our boy Tomas really knows what he's doing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:56.79,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你能不能別這麼眉飛色舞\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Perhaps you could try not to sound quite so enthused.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:58.56,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,犯罪是我的日常工作\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Crime is my day job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:08:00.89,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我…我只是很欣賞他的技術\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm-- I'm just admiring his technique.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:02.69,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,區域感知系統發現了搶劫事件\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Domain awareness caught the robbery,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:05.86,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但是沒有監控拍到托馬斯和他手下上車\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but not camera saw Tomas and his crew getting into the car,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:07.77,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,那輛車兩天前就報失了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}which was reported stolen two days ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:09.90,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,所以警察還沒確定他的身份？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}So the cops haven't ID'd him yet?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.97,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我很確定不止紐約警局\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm fairly certain that the NYPD{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.91,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,想找到他們\N{\reng_1 - 1080}isn't the only agency trying to find them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.81,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他們的作案手法\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Their modus operandi matches that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.44,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,和一個超級盜竊團伙很相似\N{\reng_1 - 1080}of a highly successful team of thieves{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:21.91,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,國際刑警組織稱之為「穿牆幫」\N{\reng_1 - 1080}that the Interpol has dubbed "The Hole In The Wall" gang{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:24.38,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,名字真形象\N{\reng_1 - 1080}for obvious reasons.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.22,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,過去七年裏\N{\reng_1 - 1080}In the past seven years,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.42,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>托馬斯和他的團伙已在四大洲</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Tomas and his team have hit over 50{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:31.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>成功盜取高價物品50餘次</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}high value targets on four continents.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:34.83,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,托馬斯真是個壞小子呢\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Mmm, so Tomas is a real bad boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:39.66,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這意味著他可能是行兇者\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Which means that he is probably our perpetrator.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:42.00,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這種人為了得手下一個目標\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Guy like this might be willing to kill{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.00,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,可能會不惜殺人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}to take down his next score.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.40,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們的目標也可能是\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Or our target might be someone{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.91,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,某個已經知道托馬斯秘密的人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}who already knows Tomas' secrets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:51.41,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,馬爾科·約弗提克是托馬斯的團伙中\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Marko Jevtic was the only member of Tomas' crew{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:53.01,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,唯一被捕過的人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}to ever get caught.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:55.78,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,在布拉格作案後被警方逮捕\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Picked up by the police after a robbery in Prague.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:57.28,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,被捕十小時後，在拘留所死亡\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Ten hours later, he died in custody{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.68,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,死因可疑\N{\reng_1 - 1080}under suspicious circumstances.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:03.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,也許托馬斯不惜殺了自己的同夥\N{\reng_1 - 1080}So maybe Tomas isn't above bumping off one of his own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:05.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他們這夥人可不靠譜\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Well, they're not the most trustworthy bunch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,麥克斯·達爾格倫\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Max Dahlgren{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:10.16,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,亨裏克·冷菲爾德\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and Henrik Lengfelder,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:13.93,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,都有詳細的案底記錄\N{\reng_1 - 1080}both had well-documented issues with authority.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:17.00,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,卡佳·羅欽科有長期吸毒的歷史\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And Katya Rodchenko has a long history of drug abuse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:18.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,看來我們無意間抓了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It appears that we have inadvertently captured{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:21.14,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,一夥臭名昭著的罪犯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}a group of notorious criminals.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:24.27,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,要不把他們交給國際刑警然後就收工？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Should we turn them over to Interpol and call it a day?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:26.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們來這兒是阻止犯罪的，好嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We're here to stop violence, okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不是為了追回被盜的珠寶\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Not recover stolen jewels.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:30.45,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,如果我們沒搞清楚托馬斯的陰謀就撤了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}If we move before we know what Tomas is up to,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.95,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,一旦事態惡化\N{\reng_1 - 1080}then this whole thing could go sideways,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:33.35,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們就來不及阻止了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and we'll miss our chance to stop it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,而且你也就沒機會欣賞他了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Plus you won't get to look at him anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:37.39,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你找死嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Are you trying to make me kill you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.85,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們還是專注於\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Let's try to stay focused on the murder{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:41.12,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,克羅阿先生正在策劃的謀殺吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}that Mr. Koroa is poised to commit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,要搞清楚他的計劃\N{\reng_1 - 1080}To uncover his plans,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.69,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們得安插人進去\N{\reng_1 - 1080}we would need to have a man on the inside.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:47.33,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這種情況的話，女人更合適\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Or in this case, a woman.{\r}
