Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.09,0:28:02.12,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>馬爾科？</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Marko?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.13,0:28:03.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,馬爾科·約弗提克？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Marko Jevtic?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.59,0:28:05.86,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>死在布拉格的搭檔？</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The partner that died in Prague?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.86,0:28:07.53,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,等等，你沒殺他嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Wait, didn't you kill that guy?{\r}
