Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.73,0:28:11.63,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們在他被抓之後想把他救出來的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We tried to spring Marko out after he got caught,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.63,0:28:13.97,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但那樣太冒險了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but it was too risky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.97,0:28:17.60,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,所以要麼他是一具保存完好的屍體\N{\reng_1 - 1080}So either he's a really well-preserved corpse,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.61,0:28:19.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,要麼就是他裝死逃出來了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}or he escaped by faking his own death.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.88,0:28:21.38,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>馬爾科認為我們置他的生死於不顧</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Marko thinks we left him to rot,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.38,0:28:23.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這場騙局就是他的報復\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and this whole double-cross is his revenge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.75,0:28:25.31,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,報復不報復的，約弗提克手裏有\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Revenge or not, Jevtic is in possession{\r}
