Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.62,0:28:27.95,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我很想知道\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and I would very much like to know{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.95,0:28:29.58,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>他打算用來幹什麼</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}what he intends to do with it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.39,0:28:34.49,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我的買家剛轉了一半的款項\N{\reng_1 - 1080}My buyer just transferred half the money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.49,0:28:36.32,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,包裹交付之後再轉剩餘的一半\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We get the rest when the package is delivered.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.33,0:28:38.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>我們午夜行動</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We move at midnight.{\r}
