Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.96,0:28:42.66,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,來想出辦法搶劫這個地方\N{\reng_1 - 1080}to figure out how to rob this place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.43,0:28:47.57,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們還有個麻煩，哈羅德\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We have another problem, Harold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.57,0:28:50.24,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我看見了一個相關方的特工\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm looking at an operative from the relevant side.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.24,0:28:51.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>政府特工？</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}A government agent?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.84,0:28:53.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你確定嗎？你怎麼知道的？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Are you certain? How do you know?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.84,0:28:55.58,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,因為是我訓練的他\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Because I trained him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.58,0:28:58.61,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>戴文·格萊斯，深紅6α</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Devon Grice, Crimson Six Alpha.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.61,0:29:01.45,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我認識他和他搭檔\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I know him and his partner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.45,0:29:02.98,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,既然病毒在馬爾科手上\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now that Marko has the virus,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.98,0:29:06.65,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,所有的破事都變成相關事件了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}this whole damn thing just went relevant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.32,0:29:22.67,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>上行線路正常</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Uplink's good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.68,0:29:24.94,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,國安局信號在線\N{\reng_1 - 1080}NSA feeds online.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.94,0:29:28.91,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你懷念過過去嗎，布魯克斯？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You ever miss the old days, Brooks?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.92,0:29:29.91,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,懷念舊系統？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The old system?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.92,0:29:31.22,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.22,0:29:32.75,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,「搜查者2.0」比舊系統\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Research 2.0 targets more threats{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.75,0:29:34.25,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,標記出更多的威脅\N{\reng_1 - 1080}than the old system ever did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.25,0:29:35.35,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,就是這個問題\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Well, that's just it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.35,0:29:36.55,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,以前是我們負責確定目標\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Back then, we did the targeting,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.56,0:29:37.95,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,檢查情報\N{\reng_1 - 1080}had to scrutinize our own intel,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.96,0:29:39.96,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們自己思考\N{\reng_1 - 1080}think for ourselves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.96,0:29:42.63,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們選中一個目標的時候，知道是為什麼\N{\reng_1 - 1080}When we lit up a target, we knew why.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.63,0:29:45.60,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,現在不是給我們號碼去調查他們了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now instead of numbers to investigate,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.60,0:29:48.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,而是給我們號碼去幹掉他們\N{\reng_1 - 1080}we just get numbers to kill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.97,0:29:52.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你不覺得奇怪嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You don't think that's strange?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.87,0:29:54.94,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,付錢給我們不是讓我們思考的，格萊斯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We don't get paid to think, Grice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.94,0:29:56.97,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,而且操控者不會喜歡你這些話的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And Control wouldn't like what you're saying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.97,0:29:59.54,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你還記得靛藍5號吧？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You remember what happened to Indigo Five, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.54,0:30:03.15,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我聽說肖活下來了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I heard Shaw lived to fight another day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.15,0:30:04.75,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,沒人活下來\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Nobody lives,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.75,0:30:07.45,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,而且問問題從來都沒好下場\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and no good comes of asking questions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.45,0:30:13.82,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們的命令就是要消滅所有目標\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Our orders are to eliminate all targets{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.82,0:30:16.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,徹底銷毀這個病毒\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and destroy every last drop of this virus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.26,0:30:18.63,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們晚上十點行動\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We strike at 2200.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.43,0:30:24.57,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但如果相關方要處理病毒\N{\reng_1 - 1080}But if the relevant side is taking care of the virus,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.57,0:30:26.50,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,也許就不用我們了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}perhaps our work here is done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.50,0:30:28.57,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>現在是撒瑪利亞在給政府提供</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now that Samaritan is providing the relevant numbers{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.57,0:30:29.97,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>相關號碼</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}to the government,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.97,0:30:31.67,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,任何與那些特工的衝突\N{\reng_1 - 1080}any encounter with those operatives{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.68,0:30:33.11,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,都可能輕易升級為\N{\reng_1 - 1080}could easily escalate{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.11,0:30:35.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,與撒瑪利亞特工之間的紛爭\N{\reng_1 - 1080}into a run-in with Samaritan's agents.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.18,0:30:38.11,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,為什麼要冒不必要的風險暴露我們的行動呢？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Why expose our operation to unnecessary risk?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.12,0:30:40.52,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>因為我知道相關方是如何工作的，芬奇</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Because I know how the relevant side works, Finch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.52,0:30:41.92,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,而且我認識格萊斯和布魯克斯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And I know Grice and Brooks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.92,0:30:43.59,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,殺了馬爾科和他的手下之後\N{\reng_1 - 1080}After they kill Marko and his men,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.59,0:30:45.35,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他們還會追蹤每一個\N{\reng_1 - 1080}they're gonna track down everyone involved{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.35,0:30:46.82,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,參與了偷竊病毒的人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}in stealing the virus,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.82,0:30:48.52,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,也會把他們都殺掉\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and they're gonna kill them too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.52,0:30:52.09,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,托馬斯想要糾正這一切\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Tomas is trying to make this right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.10,0:30:53.33,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他也許是個罪犯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}He may be a criminal,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.33,0:30:56.03,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但罪不至死\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but he doesn't deserve to die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.03,0:30:58.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>這不也是我們來這裏的目的嗎？</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And isn't that what we're here for,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.20,0:31:00.27,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,救他的性命\N{\reng_1 - 1080}to save his life?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.27,0:31:02.00,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,她說倒你了，芬奇\N{\reng_1 - 1080}She's got you there, Finch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.00,0:31:04.77,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,而且，蘇聯人把馬爾堡病毒作為武器亂來過\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Besides, the Soviets messed around with weaponizing Marburg.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.77,0:31:06.54,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,美國人還沒有\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The Americans never did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.54,0:31:07.94,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你真的想讓相關方\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Do you really want the relevant side{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.94,0:31:09.51,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,拿到那個病毒？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}to get their hands on that virus?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.51,0:31:11.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,或者讓他們把病毒交給撒瑪利亞？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Or let them turn it over to Samaritan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.71,0:31:14.62,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>唯一能保證病毒被徹底銷毀的辦法</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}The only way to make sure those vials get destroyed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.62,0:31:16.52,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,就是我們自己來\N{\reng_1 - 1080}is to do it ourselves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.52,0:31:18.28,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好吧，我們就來犯罪吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Fine, we'll commit your felony.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.29,0:31:19.85,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不過不幸的是\N{\reng_1 - 1080}But unfortunately,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.86,0:31:22.79,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我還要先參加另外一項犯罪活動\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I have another criminal act to attend to first.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.79,0:31:25.13,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,葛洛弗女士，我馬上就到\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Ms. Groves, I'm on my way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.13,0:31:27.56,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>很好，威爾金斯正要離開</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Good, Wilkins is about to leave for the night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.23,0:31:35.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這就開始打印了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And now we are cooking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.07,0:31:37.34,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,大家幹得好\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Nice work, you guys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.34,0:31:39.71,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,第一批應該明早就能完成\N{\reng_1 - 1080}First batch should be done by morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.37,0:32:43.43,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>撒瑪利亞看不見了，哈羅德，上吧</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Samaritan's blind, Harold. You're up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.41,0:32:49.54,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,正在進入系統\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Accessing the system.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.54,0:32:52.38,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,大約需要十分鐘\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'll need about ten minutes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.58,0:32:57.82,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,什麼事？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.82,0:32:59.48,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我收到一條短信，說如果我五分鐘內\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I got a text offering me 3,000 bucks{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.48,0:33:01.95,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,修好這裏的網絡就能拿到三千塊\N{\reng_1 - 1080}if I can fix your internet in the next five minutes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.95,0:33:03.72,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我不想催你，哈羅德\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I don't want to rush you, Harold,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.72,0:33:05.79,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但是撒瑪利亞已經找上來了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but I think Samaritan's onto us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.79,0:33:07.83,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,真意外，葛洛弗女士\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Surprisingly, Ms. Groves,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.83,0:33:09.83,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這對我集中精神毫無幫助\N{\reng_1 - 1080}that does not help me concentrate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.71,0:33:27.94,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,哈羅德，我要做點你不喜歡的事\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Harold, I'm about to do something you're not gonna like.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.28,0:33:32.55,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不需要，我搞定了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}No need. I'm done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.99,0:33:46.73,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,好吧，進去，拿到病毒，走人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Okay, get in, get the virus, get out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.73,0:33:51.50,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,下個月在巴塞羅那還有活兒\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Got a job in Barcelona next month.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.50,0:33:54.50,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,如果我們能過這關，你就跟我一起幹吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}If we live through this, you should join me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.50,0:33:57.51,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我已經有活兒了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I already have a job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.51,0:33:59.64,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,很詭異的工作，給的也很少\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It's weird, the pay sucks,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.64,0:34:02.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但是…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but, uh...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.18,0:34:05.15,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們需要你這樣的人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}we could use a guy like you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.15,0:34:08.65,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我到位了，肖女士\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm in position, Ms. Shaw.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.65,0:34:10.35,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我已經繞過大樓防火牆\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I've circumvented the building's firewall{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.35,0:34:13.42,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,進入了安保系統\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and accessed their security.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.42,0:34:14.66,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,隨時可以行動\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Ready when you are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.53,0:34:27.33,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,指揮官，我們正忙\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Command, we're in the middle of something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.34,0:34:28.67,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>我們知道，深紅6號</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We're aware, Crimson Six.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.67,0:34:30.30,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>但剛接到新命令</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}But new orders just came through.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.31,0:34:33.01,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>你們要消滅所有目標</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You are instructed to eliminate all targets{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.01,0:34:34.77,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>保護病毒</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and secure the vials.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.78,0:34:36.68,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們之前的命令是摧毀病毒，不是…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Our orders were to destroy that virus, not--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.68,0:34:39.31,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你們要保護病毒並完好無損地帶回\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You are to secure the vials and turn them over intact{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.32,0:34:41.95,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>移交給聯繫人，他已經在路上了</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}to a contact already en route.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.95,0:34:43.82,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,誰的聯繫人？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}A contact for whom?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.82,0:34:45.69,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>你不必知道，深紅6號</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}That's need-to-know, Crimson Six.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.69,0:34:47.05,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>你明白了嗎？</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Do you acknowledge?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.06,0:34:48.39,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>重複，你明白了嗎？</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Repeat, do you acknowledge?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.39,0:34:50.12,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Acknowledged.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.87,0:34:59.50,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們沒被攝像頭拍到吧？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We're not on camera, are we, Finch?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.50,0:35:01.13,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>還沒有</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Not yet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.14,0:35:02.54,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,而且樓裏還有別人\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And you should know that you're not alone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.54,0:35:04.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>相關方的人</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Our friends from the relevant side{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.21,0:35:06.57,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,也在樓裏\N{\reng_1 - 1080}are in the building.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.57,0:35:09.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,意味著中央指揮正在遠程指揮\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Which means Central Command will be running op-sec{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.04,0:35:11.54,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他們的行動\N{\reng_1 - 1080}from a remote location.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.55,0:35:13.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>如果你能看見我們</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}If you see us,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.18,0:35:14.85,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他們也能\N{\reng_1 - 1080}so will they.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.85,0:35:16.58,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,所以我在循環播放安保錄像\N{\reng_1 - 1080}That's why I'm looping the security feeds{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.58,0:35:18.42,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,來掩護你們\N{\reng_1 - 1080}to cover your tracks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.01,0:35:48.85,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>馬爾科的保險櫃在你左邊第五個</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Marko's vault is fifth on your left.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.85,0:35:51.25,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,務必要快，其他人離得不遠了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And please work quickly. The others aren't far behind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.39,0:36:02.79,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不錯嘛\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Not bad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.80,0:36:04.76,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,那你的魔法之手\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now, how are those magic fingers{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.76,0:36:06.30,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,要怎麼打開那個呢？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}gonna open that one?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.78,0:36:22.78,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>抱歉，朋友</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Sorry, my friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.49,0:36:29.62,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我可不像你，不會把重要的東西落下\N{\reng_1 - 1080}But unlike you, I don't leave important things behind.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.29,0:36:34.83,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我知道你會來取病毒，托馬斯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I knew you would come for these, Tomas,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.83,0:36:36.63,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,就像我知道如果你知道目標是什麼\N{\reng_1 - 1080}just like I knew you would never be bold enough{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.63,0:36:38.93,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,絕對沒膽去偷\N{\reng_1 - 1080}to steal them if you really knew the score,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.93,0:36:40.90,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,倒也方便了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}which is convenient.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.90,0:36:43.23,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我的買家想讓病毒\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You see, my buyer wants the virus delivered{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.24,0:36:44.90,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,在紐約擴散\N{\reng_1 - 1080}right here in New York City.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.90,0:36:46.67,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,還有什麼能比兩個\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And who better to start a pandemic{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.67,0:36:49.91,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,健康的活體宿主更合適？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}than two healthy human hosts?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.90,0:37:05.83,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>我們打算要救你出來的，馬爾科</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We were planning to get you out, Marko,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.83,0:37:07.50,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但聽說你死了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but we got word that you died.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.50,0:37:09.13,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,如果我知道你還…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}If I had known that you were still--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.14,0:37:11.50,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你知道偽裝死亡有多疼嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You know how painful it is to fake your own death?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.51,0:37:15.17,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你知道模擬心臟驟停的毒素\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What the toxins that simulate cardiac arrest{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.18,0:37:17.41,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,對身體有什麼傷害嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}do to your health?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.11,0:37:23.08,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這個會更糟\N{\reng_1 - 1080}This will be worse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.08,0:37:24.75,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>我不想打擾你，肖女士</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I hate to trouble you, Ms. Shaw,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.75,0:37:26.92,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>但你的相關方夥伴</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but your counterparts from the relevant side{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.92,0:37:29.25,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,馬上就要讓目前的情況\N{\reng_1 - 1080}are about to turn this perilous situation{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.26,0:37:31.36,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,更加危險混亂\N{\reng_1 - 1080}into something dangerously chaotic,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.36,0:37:33.42,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,可能會有點吵\N{\reng_1 - 1080}so it may get a bit loud.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.20,0:37:47.17,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,動手，約翰\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Now, John!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.17,0:37:48.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}What the--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.81,0:37:56.45,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這些是什麼人？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Who the hell are these guys?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.45,0:37:58.12,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,收到命令殺人的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Highly trained government assassins{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.12,0:38:00.52,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,訓練有素的政府殺手\N{\reng_1 - 1080}with orders to kill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.75,0:38:05.96,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你讓我跟你幹這活兒太不地道了啊，哥們\N{\reng_1 - 1080}It's not cool you ask me to do this stuff with you, man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.96,0:38:07.26,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不地道！\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Not cool!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.44,0:38:24.77,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,承認吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Admit it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.78,0:38:26.78,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,咱倆搭活也不錯\N{\reng_1 - 1080}we're not bad together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.45,0:38:31.88,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你說這話是因為我救了你的小命\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You're just saying that because I saved your ass.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.88,0:38:33.12,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,得了吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.12,0:38:35.52,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你，我，巴塞羅那\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You, me, Barcelona.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.52,0:38:37.45,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,160萬\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Score worth 1.6 mil.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.46,0:38:40.12,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你真的不想來？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You sure you won't come?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.12,0:38:43.69,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你，我，在這，一分錢沒有\N{\reng_1 - 1080}You, me, here, no pay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.69,0:38:45.23,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,最終都會死翹翹\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We both eventually wind up dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.23,0:38:46.96,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你真的不想留下？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Are you sure you won't stay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.63,0:38:51.63,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,肖女士和克羅阿先生正在離開，約翰\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Ms. Shaw and Mr. Koroa are leaving, John.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.64,0:38:53.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>而且考慮到警察正在趕來</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And considering that the police are en route,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.74,0:38:57.54,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,也許你們也該現在撤離\N{\reng_1 - 1080}now might be a good time for you to make your exit too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.74,0:39:31.37,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不許動\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Freeze.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.87,0:39:35.28,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>肖？</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Shaw?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.78,0:39:41.88,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.92,0:39:45.62,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,快走！\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Go!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.24,0:40:05.07,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我接到電話說二樓起火了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I got a call about a fire on the second floor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.07,0:40:07.31,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,205室的3D打印機沒事吧？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Suite 205, the 3-D printers, are they okay?{\r}
