Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.38,0:40:12.65,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不\N{\reng_1 - 1080}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.65,0:40:14.15,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不要啊\N{\reng_1 - 1080}No, no, no, no, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.15,0:40:17.25,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,1120萬化成了灰\N{\reng_1 - 1080}11.2 million up in smoke.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.25,0:40:19.08,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,州長再給他錢勢必會引起注意\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I doubt the Governor could give him any more money{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.09,0:40:22.29,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,撒瑪利亞可不希望這樣\N{\reng_1 - 1080}without attracting attention Samaritan doesn't want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.29,0:40:24.96,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,現在，我種下的蠕蟲病毒已經\N{\reng_1 - 1080}By now, the worm I planted will have destroyed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.96,0:40:26.73,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,<i>毀了威爾金斯所有設計的備份</i>\N{\reng_1 - 1080}every last copy of Wilkins' design.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.73,0:40:30.60,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這樣孩子們就沒有平板了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}So no tablets for the kids.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.60,0:40:32.30,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,任務完成\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Mission accomplished.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.30,0:40:36.64,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,經典台詞啊\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Famous last words.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.64,0:40:38.64,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我破壞打印機的時候\N{\reng_1 - 1080}While I was sabotaging the printers,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.64,0:40:42.27,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,瞟了一眼平板的操作系統\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I took a quick look at the tablet's OS.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.28,0:40:44.74,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,有一條代碼好像有點可疑\N{\reng_1 - 1080}There was maybe one suspicious line of code,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.75,0:40:48.81,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我甚至都不確定它有不正當意圖\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and I'm not even sure it had any nefarious purpose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.82,0:40:51.28,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,哈羅德，你真的認為撒瑪利亞\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Harold, you really think Samaritan{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.29,0:40:52.75,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,造那些東西\N{\reng_1 - 1080}was building those things{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.75,0:40:54.92,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,是因為它發善心？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}out of the goodness of its own heart?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.92,0:40:56.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,當卡斯特羅掌權古巴的時候\N{\reng_1 - 1080}When Castro was coming to power in Cuba,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.99,0:40:59.52,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他做的第一件事就是建學校，好的學校\N{\reng_1 - 1080}the first thing he did was build schools, good schools,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.53,0:41:01.93,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這樣人們就會愛戴他\N{\reng_1 - 1080}so that the people would love him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.93,0:41:07.80,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我知道撒瑪利亞的動機與道德無關\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I know that Samaritan's motives are amoral at best,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.80,0:41:10.50,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但威爾金斯先生想做的事\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but the thing that Mr. Wilkins was trying to do{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.50,0:41:13.27,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,絕對是善事，而我們就這麼給毀了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}was an absolute good, and we destroyed it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.27,0:41:15.84,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我不知道我們會變成什麼樣，葛洛弗女士\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm not sure what we're becoming, Ms. Groves,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.84,0:41:17.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,而這讓我思考…\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and it does make me wonder...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.04,0:41:18.38,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們願意以正義之名\N{\reng_1 - 1080}How much wrong are we willing to do{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.38,0:41:20.54,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,行多少邪惡？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}in the name of right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.66,0:41:34.22,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我知道耳朵裏沒有機器的聲音\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I'm sure not having the machine{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.23,0:41:35.99,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,糟透了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}in your ear anymore sucks and all,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.99,0:41:37.89,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但能夠偷襲你\N{\reng_1 - 1080}but it is pretty great{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.90,0:41:41.03,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,感覺還是挺爽的\N{\reng_1 - 1080}finally being able to sneak up on you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.03,0:41:44.30,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我為快樂而活\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I live to amuse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.30,0:41:46.34,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,托馬斯呢？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Where's Tomas?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.34,0:41:48.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,在去巴塞羅那的路上\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Halfway to Barcelona.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.04,0:41:49.87,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,他開了特別誘人的條件\N{\reng_1 - 1080}He gave me a pretty hard sell,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.87,0:41:51.21,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,想讓我入伙\N{\reng_1 - 1080}trying to get me to go with him,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.21,0:41:54.24,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,有那麼一秒鐘我差點就同意了\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and for a hot second, I almost did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.25,0:41:58.18,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,但是呢？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}But?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.18,0:42:01.85,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我覺得這裏有我在意的東西吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I guess there are things I care about here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.85,0:42:06.56,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,這就是你來見我的原因？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}And is that why you came to see me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.56,0:42:08.19,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\reng_1 - 1080}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.19,0:42:10.39,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我需要你翻譯一下芬奇的說明書\N{\reng_1 - 1080}I need you to translate Finch's instructions{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.39,0:42:12.43,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,看看怎麼消滅病毒\N{\reng_1 - 1080}on how to destroy the virus.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.43,0:42:15.16,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,全是高級詞兒\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Dude never met a five-syllable word he didn't like.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.17,0:42:17.20,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,要全面消毒\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Full decontamination.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.20,0:42:21.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,可能得搞一整晚\N{\reng_1 - 1080}This could take all night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.21,0:42:25.94,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們還沒找到病毒\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We haven't recovered the virus yet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.94,0:42:28.04,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,你確定我們不應該繼續追蹤嗎？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Are you sure we shouldn't be tracking it down?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.04,0:42:30.25,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,我們有新命令\N{\reng_1 - 1080}We have new orders{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.25,0:42:33.72,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,還有一列新號碼要我們去南美搞定\N{\reng_1 - 1080}and a list of new numbers to take care of in South America.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.72,0:42:38.02,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,問問題從來都沒好下場\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Nothing good comes out of asking questions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.19,0:42:40.19,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,記得吧？\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Remember?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.91,0:43:06.10,chs_2 - 1080,,0,0,0,,開始吧\N{\reng_1 - 1080}Go.{\r}
